# ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryDiscovered

**Case**

The session discovered an accessory.

## Declaration

```swift
case accessoryDiscovered
```

## Discussion

Your app only receives this event if your picker uses the [doc://com.apple.AccessorySetupKit/documentation/AccessorySetupKit/ASPickerDisplaySettings/Options-swift.struct/filterDiscoveryResults] option.
